### PPTX bank — uncommitted corpus of real decks for ad-hoc agent use
# (probing OOXML, debugging round-trip, fixture candidates). Distinct from the
# curated, hash-pinned harness inputs in test/read/fixtures/. Track only the
# README so the convention stays self-documenting; ignore all .pptx bytes.
# Use `dir/*` (not `dir/`) + a negation so git can re-include the README —
# it cannot re-include a file inside a fully-excluded directory.
/pptx-bank/*
!/pptx-bank/README.md

### OOXML-Validator binary (downloaded by tools/ooxml-validator/install.sh)
tools/ooxml-validator/bin/

### Claude Code local/runtime files (shared config like .claude/settings.json stays tracked)
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/*.lock
# Local junction/symlink mirroring .agents/skills/ for Skill-registry discovery; canonical source lives in .agents/
.claude/skills/
